Amazon MX Player presents

About Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, a small-town boxer from Safidon, enters Delhi‚Äôs elite St. Collins college to fulfill his brother‚Äôs dream of becoming a polished, English-speaking graduate. Amidst bullies, culture shocks, and class divides, he falls for Antara Shukla ‚Äî a senior with political aspirations and far out of his league. When a humiliating dare collides with his growing feelings and a family crisis back home, Rajveer must fight harder than ever ‚Äî this time, not for glory, but for love, dignity, and survival.

#Netflix #StrangerThings #StrangerThings5

üé• Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
Experience the beginning of the end with this Stranger Things Season 5 VOLUME 2 Trailer, bringing a final look at the epic conclusion to Netflix‚Äôs biggest series. Featuring fan-favorite characters like Eleven (Millie Bobby Brown), Mike Wheeler (Finn Wolfhard), Will Byers (Noah Schnapp), Lucas (Caleb McLaughlin), Max (Sadie Sink), Dustin (Gaten Matarazzo), Robin (Maya Hawke), Steve Harrington (Joe Keery), Nancy (Natalia Dyer), Jonathan (Charlie Heaton), Joyce Byers (Winona Ryder), and Chief Hopper (David Harbour), the final season sets the stage for a showdown with Vecna (Jamie Campbell Bower). This concept trailer captures the tone of the Stranger Things Season 5 Official Teaser, Final Season Trailer 2, and all the emotional stakes fans have been waiting for as Netflix‚Äôs iconic story reaches its climactic end.

The inspiration behind this video:
The long-awaited Stranger Things Season 5 VOLUME 2 Trailer has arrived, giving fans their deepest look yet at the final chapter of Netflix‚Äôs biggest phenomenon. As the Stranger Things Season 5 story pushes toward its epic conclusion, the new footage expands on what we saw in the Stranger Things 5 Final Season Trailer 2 and the Stranger Things 5 Official Teaser, delivering darker stakes, emotional reunions, and the return of the Upside Down‚Äôs deadliest threat, Vecna. With anticipation at an all-time high, viewers around the world are searching for every detail connected to the Stranger Things Final Trailer and the final showdown ahead.

The cast‚ÄîMillie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Noah Schnapp, Caleb McLaughlin, Sadie Sink, Gaten Matarazzo, Maya Hawke, Joe Keery, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Cara Buono, Winona Ryder, and David Harbour‚Äîreturns for their biggest fight yet, alongside Jamie Campbell Bower as Vecna. Fan-favorite characters like Chief Hopper, Eleven, Mike Wheeler, Dustin, Lucas, Max, Jonathan Byers, Joyce Byers, Will Byers, and Steve Harrington take center stage as the Hawkins crew prepares for war. Netflix is setting the stage for a massive finale, supported by global excitement around the Stranger Things Trailer, St5 Trailer, and every new look released.

Trailer communities such as Rotten Tomatoes TV, Teaser PRO, FilmSpot Trailer, MovieGasm, KinoCheck, EmergencyAwesome, and IGN TV Trailer, along with countless TV Promos, continue to break down every frame. With growing interest in Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2, the Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2 Trailer, Stranger Things Season 5 Part 2, the Stranger Things Season 5 Part 2 Trailer, and the evolving narrative teased in the Stranger Things 5 Trailer Volume 2, fans are preparing for a finale that promises to be unforgettable. This is the final battle for Hawkins‚Äîand the world is watching.

Bersiaplah untuk akhir epik serial horor fiksi ilmiah Netflix yang dicintai ini dengan trailer Stranger Things Musim 5. Dijadwalkan tayang perdana pada November 2025, musim terakhir ini menjanjikan puncak yang mendebarkan dari saga Hawkins. Setelah penundaan akibat pemogokan industri, produksi selesai pada Desember 2024, dan pascaproduksi berjalan lebih cepat dari jadwal. Duffer Brothers telah menciptakan musim ambisius yang digambarkan sebagai "delapan film blockbuster," dengan fokus pada kedalaman emosi dan aksi berisiko tinggi.

Narasi berpusat pada pertempuran pamungkas kru Hawkins melawan Vecna, menggali lebih dalam misteri Upside Down. Nantikan kembalinya ke akar seri ini dengan perpaduan dinamika awal dan pengembangan karakter yang signifikan, terutama menyoroti perjalanan Will menuju kedewasaan. Musim ini juga akan mengeksplorasi sifat Upside Down yang menakutkan dan membeku, berpotensi menggabungkan lompatan waktu untuk menyesuaikan dengan para pemain yang menua.

Para pemeran utama kembali, termasuk Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, David Harbour, Winona Ryder, Gaten Matarazzo, Caleb McLaughlin, Noah Schnapp, Sadie Sink, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Joe Keery, Maya Hawke, Priah Ferguson, Brett Gelman, Cara Buono, dan Jamie Campbell Bower. Tambahan baru seperti Linda Hamilton dan Amybeth McNulty bergabung, menambah dinamika segar pada cerita. Delapan judul episode yang telah dikonfirmasi, termasuk "The Crawl," "The Vanishing of‚Ä¶," dan "The Rightside Up," mengisyaratkan musim yang penuh intrik dan petualangan. Jangan lewatkan akhir yang klimaks dan penuh nostalgia dari serial ikonis ini.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚óÅ Di kanal kami, kami membuat mashup trailer ‚ñ∑ Mashup trailer, juga dikenal sebagai trailer recut, dibuat dengan mengumpulkan berbagai cuplikan film dari satu atau lebih film dan menyuntingnya kembali untuk membentuk trailer baru. Mashup ini sering kali menggambarkan film yang tidak ada atau mengubah genre film yang sudah ada. Sebagai karya turunan yang didefinisikan dalam Undang-Undang Hak Cipta Amerika Serikat 17 U.S.C. ¬ß 101, karya ini mungkin dilindungi dari klaim hak cipta berdasarkan doktrin penggunaan wajar.

Mashup trailer bukan sekadar bentuk kreativitas digital yang dihasilkan pengguna, tetapi juga cara unik untuk membangun antusiasme terhadap rilis film mendatang, melengkapi trailer film resmi. Sementara trailer tradisional hanya memberikan bocoran plot dan membangkitkan sensasi, mashup buatan penggemar memungkinkan penonton untuk memberikan sentuhan sinematik mereka sendiri pada rekaman yang sudah ada. Kebebasan berkreasi ini dapat menyoroti aktor tertentu, menekankan alur cerita tertentu, atau bahkan mengubah genre film sepenuhnya.

snippet.title: Kehna Hi Kya (Lyrical Video) Chitra | A. R. Rahman | Arvind Swamy, Manisha Koirala | Mehboob|Bombay
snippet.description:
#Revibe invites you to immerse yourself in the timeless classic "#KehnaHiKya" by the mellifluous #Chitra, featured in the iconic movie "#Bombay." This musical gem is a journey into the heart of melody and emotion, a song that transcends the boundaries of time and language, leaving an indelible mark on the soul.

Chitra's enchanting vocals in "Kehna Hi Kya" effortlessly convey the depths of love and longing, creating a musical experience that resonates with every listener. With its poetic lyrics and evocative composition, this song has become an anthem of romance and a testament to the power of music to touch the heart.

Credits: 
Singer: Chitra
Music: A. R. Rahman
Lyrics: Mehboob
Movie: Bombay

snippet.title: Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad Lyrical | Lata Mangeshkar | Suresh Wadkar | Prem Rog | Rishi Kapoor
snippet.description:
Relive the magic of classic Bollywood with the soulful duet ‚ÄúMeri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad‚Äù sung by the legendary Lata Mangeshkar and Suresh Wadkar. Featured in the iconic movie Prem Rog starring Rishi Kapoor, this lyrical video brings out the emotion, romance, and timeless charm of old Hindi melodies. üé∂‚ù§Ô∏è

Don‚Äôt forget to like, share for more musical journeys through Bollywood‚Äôs golden era. üëâ Subscribe to Our channel:  https://youtube.com/@SureshWadkarOldSongs-m5c?si=NbrZmfXqKqNRco1a 

Song Credits:
Song: Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad
Artist: Lata Mangeshkar, Suresh Wadkar
Music: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Amir Qazalbash

Film Credits:
Film: Prem Rog
Director: Raj Kapoor
Producer: Randhir Kapoor
Star Cast: Rishi Kapoor, Padmini Kolhapure, Shammi Kapoor, Nanda, Tanuja, Kulbhushan Kharbanda, Om Prakash, Bindu, Vijayendra, Kiran Vairale, Raza Murad

 Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad Song Lyrics 
meree kismat me too nahee shaayad, kyon teraa intjaar karata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo
aaj samajee hoo pyaar ko shaayad, aaj mai tujhako pyaar karatee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

sochata hoo ke meree aankho ne, kyon sajaaye the pyaar ke sapne
tujhase maangee thee ek khushee maine, tune gham bhee nahee diye apane
jindagee bojh ban gayee abb toh, abb toh jita hoo aur naa marata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo

abb naa tute yeh pyaar ke rishte, abb yeh rishte sanbhaalane honge
meree raaho se tujhako kal kee tarah, dukh ke kaante nikaalane honge
mil naa jaye khushee ke raste me, gam kee parchhayeeyo se daratee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

dil nahee ikhtiyaar me mere, jaan jaayegee pyaar me tere
tujhase milane kee aas hain aa jaa, meree duniya uadas hain aa jaa
pyaar shaayad isiko kahate hai, har ghadee bekaraar rahata hoo
raat din teree yaad aatee hai, raat din intjaar karatee hoo

snippet.title: #Video | Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi |Godfather |#Khesari Lal Yadav #Priyanka | New Bhojpuri Song 2025
snippet.description:
"Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi" is the latest romantic Bhojpuri song of 2025, released under Times Music Bhojpuri from the upcoming movie "Godfather." Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, this Bhojpuri DJ song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

snippet.title: THORATT - SHOOT | OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO | PROD. BY FLAMBOY
snippet.description:
Audio Credits :
Written & Performed By - Thoratt 
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/thoratt__/?hl=en
Music Prod  - Flamboy
Mixed & Mastered By - Jason

Video Credits :
Shot By - shotbyshahid
https://www.instagram.com/shotbyshahid_?igsh=MWRtczk5dDZ5bjUycQ==
Edit By - Aeren tunes
https://www.instagram.com/aeren.tunes?igsh=YzJpczl3eW9pb3Zn

Lyrics:
Tu  bas karte rah nakal
Main kar raha hu hustle
Flex nahi karta fir bhi hai nazar
Char dost sath tabhi hoti hai fazar
Tu lavde ka bhai mera koi nahi hai brother
Kapte hai log matlab log jate hadar 
Bad boy sha main change karu weather
Main king street ka king dursa koi nahi idhar
Sunlo koi nahi idhar 

24 saal nikala street pe 
In log se jada mila knowledge streets se
Maine bhi khaye bhot jakham
Par dekha nahi kisi ne pit be 
Teri gand jal jayegi is gane heat dekh 
Thoratt hai stage pe to spin that shit ayee
Fire hai fire hai gana yah lit dekh
Fake log fake call kare fir sim change 
Fans bole diss de kalli ko mal mat pis de
Khabri hai dost tera Ja use tip
Pray Karu do vakt ki roti aur peace de
Kala kar hu zhhaatu bat kar ijjat se 
Karma ko bolu tu bhi karam kar thik se 
khana bat ke khate hum dharam se sike 
Thug life jite par khate nahi chhinke
Kuchal diya ghamand tera kyu ki jute hai
 nike ke

Shot deke bhagte nahi vi kings hai 
Meri dark life bat kare lighting se 
 tight rakhta vers aur tight jeans hai
Clear karu cache bro hygien hai     
Bhugta na tu liya haiye jin se                              
Do do Chahere yah sare twins hai 

Brain wash kare log 
Maherbani rakho mat 
Talk shit kare log 
Toxic bhavde log 
Energy bhari hai 
Moshpit kare show 
Kam kar nar hai to 
Kis pe bhi rahem nahi I feel like a Naruto 
Bolo mat karo to 
Sukoon ki nind jab khuda ghar ho to
Yah hai bambai shehar mout hai dare to

(Hook)
Shoot shoot nakali logo se fasla rahte dur dur 
Madarchod ladke gand fad dalte goons goons 
Gang leke aatu zhatu mujhko dhun dhun 

Brutally bars matlab dhakka dayak 
Daroga ji bole tu to pakka nayak
Pushpa hai nam teri Satta gayab 
Yah mike ko dekhte hi thak ta gayak 
Satte baj ladka bas paise laiye ab 
Tatte bahar chat tu hai chatne layak
Mehanat se naseeb ko ghasit ke laiye ab 
Hood 19 ke kisse kayam

Paap kiye bhot hum nikale bhala karne 
Dost mere bhi sath me the gunha karne
Opps ko jara bhi dete nahi oo aa karne
Lavde Lage to lag jate dua karne 
Gada pap ka toda maine diya nahi bharne 
Ghamand apka toda maine diya chadne
Bandvali badsha bole sula karle

Savdhaan chore mere yade mare gav chan
Ladke log lete supari ai chi Gand yech nav saang
Dikhava karo mat kabhi to bhuke ko khila ke aav jaav
Land khandan mushkil khada tu tere liye jan dan
Koi kisi ka saga nahi aisa koi Mila nahi diya jo nahi daga bat man 

(Hook)
Shoot shoot nakali logo se fasla rahte dur dur 
Madarchod ladke gand fad dalte goons goons 
Gang leke aatu zhatu mujhko dhun dhun
